":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真兄弟講過大話 比人老笠又講<br />\n<br />\n琴晚又詐病啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點對得住主耶蘇基督</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一切都是神的安排</blockquote><br />\n猶大咁點？都係神既安排？神安排佢注定要出賣耶蘇</blockquote><br />\n係呢個時候，看見耶蘇被定了罪，就後悔了"},{"pid":"9b94a71e38a9334dfd55ad4716a7e6ff15c47f5f","tid":361149,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真兄弟講過大話 比人老笠又講<br />\n<br />\n琴晚又詐病啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點對得住主耶蘇基督</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一切都是神的安排</blockquote><br />\n猶大咁點？都係神既安排？神安排佢注定要出賣耶蘇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人有自由意志</blockquote><br />\n如果人有自由意志，神仲係唔係全知？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢一早知人點揀，咁只不過係假自由</blockquote><br />\n所以人 係 無 自 由 既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08d6b6396ec928db4aaf6f99077ae2a2e5cddec","tid":361149,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真兄弟講過大話 比人老笠又講<br />\n<br />\n琴晚又詐病啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點對得住主耶蘇基督</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一切都是神的安排</blockquote><br />\n猶大咁點？都係神既安排？神安排佢注定要出賣耶蘇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人有自由意志</blockquote><br />\n如果人有自由意志，神仲係唔係全知？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢一早知人點揀，咁只不過係假自由</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 「神的主權」與「人的自由」的討論往往會出現邏輯矛盾的質疑，似乎兩者並不可以共存。如果神有全權，人是不是只是「扯線布偶」？又如果人有自由，在不知下一刻的情況下可作出任何可能性的決定，神又如何維護祂的全知和全能？神的全知如果有限制，豈不是要按人的自由決定來「行下一步棋」，神的決定豈非要被人影響？"},{"pid":"849460b29c36fccf64d470e5f28d7c507b379c14","tid":361149,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:16:53.000Z","msg":"以《基督教要義》為基礎，<br />\n論預定論中「上帝的主權」與「人的自由意志」的關係<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinesetheology.com/DKChow/Predestination.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinesetheology.com%2FDKChow%2FPredestination.htm&d=%2Fn%2BpqTlSPub4HM7b6wCAsNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=d6095a68\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinesetheology.com/DKChow/Predestination.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n神賦予我們自由意志，讓我們有選擇的權利，我們所做的一切，都是出於我們自己的選擇，但神是知道的。就像你遠遠地看一個你特別特別熟悉了解的人，像父母和子女或者愛人之間，TA即將做的你都能預知到。但是，顯然你的預知並未影響TA的決定，TA的決定還是TA自己選擇的，你只是知道而已。<br />\n神的全知的確預知了我們的未來，但這不是他的決定，而是我們的決定。<br />\n<br />\n作者：知乎用戶<br />\n鏈接：<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/24030950/answer/26463903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F24030950%2Fanswer%2F26463903&d=%2Fn%2BpqTlSPub4HM7b6wCAsNWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=d808a92d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/24030950/answer/26463903</a><br />\n來源：知乎<br />\n著作權歸作者所有。商業轉載請聯繫作者獲得授權，非商業轉載請註明出處。"},{"pid":"899999147750e90781533a047d6d56edccf67ad6","tid":361149,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:25:51.000Z","msg":"因為個教本身就係大話"},{"pid":"7edc05da1f68994d6edc662972b57029c06252d6","tid":361149,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為個教本身就係大話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔好理，香港好多法官高官有錢人都信耶"},{"pid":"5a14fae456896173e9d5c257a23e3dda2a0085d1","tid":361149,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為個教本身就係大話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔好理，香港好多法官高官有錢人都信耶</blockquote><br />\n贖罪券?"},{"pid":"5ac5bccf078a0f2ecf6e91b84cdd675c7f0e0b89","tid":361149,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為個教本身就係大話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔好理，香港好多法官高官有錢人都信耶</blockquote><br />\n贖罪券?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" c